      "body" : "Bitcoin(d/qt) is known for using quite a lot of memory for database caches and indexes. I don't think it is a memory leak, you may have too little memory to run a full node.\r\n\r\nAlso in general I would recommend against using 64 bit on a machine with ~400MB of RAM if you have the choice. Due to the doubled size of pointers, there is more memory usage with 64 bit for every program.",
